  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink247-kilavi">veṟivilakkaluṟuntōḻi tamar kēṭpat talaimakaḷai viṉavuvāḷāyc colliyatu.    </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">What the confidante, who undertook the obstructing of the Veṟi-dance, spoke, as one who asked the heroine, so that her relatives could hear.
  
          
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink247">
<l>aṉṉai tanta tākuva taṟiveṉ</l>
<l>poṉṉakar varaippiṟ kaṉṉan tūkki</l>
<l>murukeṉa moḻiyu māyi</l>
<l>ṉaruvarai nāṭaṉ peyarkolō vatuvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>I know what will happen because of what mother has brought about.</l>
        <l rend="space">If the Vēlaṉ priest were to lift the Kaṉṉam image</l>
        <l>within the bounds of the golden mansion and say “Muruku,”</l>
        <l>is that the name of the man from the land of the difficult mountain?</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
